<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - USCS CUT BY MERRILL.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - USCS CUT BY MERRILL.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-08-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>Merrill Lynch said it downgraded USCS International Inc to intermediate-term accumulate from buy.</p>
<p>-- Said kept USCS as long-term buy.</p>
<p>-- Monday, USCS lost a contract with Tele-Communications Inc to rival CSG Systems Internatioanl Inc.</p>
<p>-- USCS slipped 3/8 to 18-5/8.</p>
</text>
